      "date": "2024-04-25 03:11:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe following sessions will be run for build 104365 patch 1\n\nEnforced:\n- review-ldiskfs-dne on el9.3-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and clients\n- review-dne-part-1 on el9.3-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and ubuntu2204-x86_64/ldiskfs clients\n\nMaloo Test Queue: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_queue?jobs=lustre-reviews&builds=104365&commit=Apply+Filter\nMaloo Results: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/related?jobs=lustre-reviews&builds=104365#redirect",
